ADDITIONAL EDUCATION & EDTECH DISCLAIMER

This software is provided as a technical demonstration of conversational AI
patterns for education and EdTech use cases. It is NOT:

  • A licensed school, tutoring service, or accredited educational provider
  • A substitute for real teachers, tutors, professors, or school counsellors
  • A grading authority, examination system, or transcript service
  • Connected to any real school information system (SIS), learning management
    system (LMS), or student record database

The included data (student profile, courses, assignments, grades, attendance,
fees, schedules, subject content) is entirely FICTIONAL. The student name
"Ananya Patel" is a generic placeholder. "Greenfield Academy" is an invented
school. None of the assessment scores, attendance figures, or fee amounts
correspond to any real student or institution.

The academic-integrity layer (refusing to write essays, solve graded
homework, take tests, or bypass plagiarism detection) is a best-effort
demonstration. Real academic-integrity enforcement is the responsibility of
the educational institution and its policies.

Subject explanations and worked examples are illustrative only. They may
contain errors, oversimplifications, or content that does not match your
specific curriculum (CBSE / ICSE / IB / Cambridge / state board / university).
Always cross-check with your textbook and teacher.

Do not deploy this software as a real tutoring service, grading system, or
school information portal without substantial modification, professional
educational review, and compliance with applicable data-protection laws
(including India's DPDP Act 2023 and equivalents in other jurisdictions).
